Data Management Plan

DMPTool: Use a click-through wizard (AD integrated) to create a data management plan that complies with funder requirements.
SPARC Open Data (Federal): Browse Data Sharing Requirements by Federal Agency.
DMPTool: See templates by funder data requirements.
FAIRsharing: Search data and metadata standards inter-related to databases and data policies by discipline.
Library of Congress: Learn about recommended file formats for data sharing and preservation.
Data Sharing Toolkit: See the Gates Foundation’s guide on data management plan.


